972390efb9aeedee9a1ef42e1bf12a0c.question_text: Please describe your shopping habits in detail
972390efb9aeedee9a1ef42e1bf12a0c.answer: I love shopping, it's like my therapy! I tend to browse online stores first, looking for the best deals and sales. I like to compare prices and read reviews before making a purchase. I prefer shopping in-person for clothes and shoes, trying things on is a must for me. I always have a list and budget in mind, but sometimes I can't resist a good impulse buy. Overall, I'd say I'm a pretty savvy shopper!
